JSE staff members waited for almost an hour at the reception area just to show Pravin Gordhan their support. JOHANNESBURG - Finance Minister Pravin Gordhan received a resounding welcome and cheers of support from staff members at the Johannesburg Stock Exchange (JSE) earlier today.The minister was due to address a sponsored event there.JSE staff members waited for almost an hour at the reception area just to show Gordhan their support.When he finally arrived, the members burst into cheers and applauded him.Some held up placards that read: Warning: Hands off Pravin Gordhan .Gordhan has been receiving support from a broad circle of people including members within the African National Congress for his upcoming case with the Hawks on Wednesday.(Edited by Winnie Theletsane)